Dataset: Cohere 1M (768d), Hardware: 16 vCPU / 64 GiB ECS
  - zvec (int8 quant, M=15, ef_search=180): ~16K QPS at 95%+ recall
Dataset: Cohere 10M (768d), Hardware: 16 vCPU / 64 GiB ECS
  - zvec (int8 quant, M=50, ef_search=118, refiner): ~8K QPS at 95%+ recall

Note: zvec uses int8 quantization + refiner by default in published benchmarks.
      YAMS HNSW above uses FP32 (no quantization). For a fair comparison,
      build zvec from source and rerun with YAMS_HAS_ZVEC=1.
      See third_party/sqlite-vec-cpp/BENCHMARKS.md for methodology.
